TechPath System Architecture

⸻

1. System Overview

TechPath uses a client-driven architecture where the frontend interacts directly with Supabase.

Architecture layers

Frontend: Next.js React application
Backend: Supabase API
Database: PostgreSQL database managed by Supabase

