3. Database Schema

⸻

Courses Table

Fields

id
department
course_number
course_name
description
credit_hours
difficulty_rating

Constraints

Department + course_number must be unique.

⸻

Instructors Table

Fields

id
name
department
rating
teaching_style

Constraints

Instructor name must be unique.

⸻

Sections Table

Fields

id
course_id
instructor_id
section_code
day_pattern
start_time
end_time
location
crn

Constraints

course_id must reference courses table
instructor_id must reference instructors table

start_time must be greater than or equal to 7:00 AM
end_time must be less than or equal to 9:00 PM

⸻

Course Prerequisites Table

Fields

id
course_id
prerequisite_course_id

Both fields must reference valid courses.

⸻

Schedules Table

Fields

id
name
semester
year

⸻

Schedule Sections Table

Fields

id
schedule_id
section_id

Links a schedule to the sections within it.

⸻

Careers Table

Fields

id
name

⸻

Career Schedules Table

Fields

id
career_id
schedule_id
semester_order

Defines the sequence of schedules within a career.

⸻

Course Reviews Table

Fields

id
course_id
rating
difficulty
comment

⸻

Instructor Reviews Table

Fields

id
instructor_id
rating
comment

